---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const schema = [
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Ergonomic Chair Pain for Tall People: Causes & Fixes",
    "url": "https://tallchairadvisor.com/pain-ergonomics/",
    "image": "https://tallchairadvisor.com/images/og-default.jpg",
    "datePublished": "2025-01-15",
    "dateModified": "2026-03-01",
    "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Tall Chair Advisor" },
    "publisher": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Tall Chair Advisor",
      "logo": { "@type": "ImageObject", "url": "https://tallchairadvisor.com/images/og-default.jpg" }
    }
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://tallchairadvisor.com/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Pain & Ergonomics", "item": "https://tallchairadvisor.com/pain-ergonomics/" }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Layout
  title="Ergonomic Chair Pain for Tall People: Causes & Fixes | Tall Chair Advisor"
  description="How poor chair ergonomics causes pain in tall people and which specific chair dimensions address back, knee, and leg pain for users 6'0\" and taller."
  schema={schema}
>
  <header class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-secondary/30">
    <div class="container-article text-center">
      <h1 class="text-balance">Pain & Ergonomics</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto animate-slide-up">
        Understanding how chair dimensions directly cause specific pain points for tall users
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="container-wide py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <p class="text-body text-center">
        When a chair doesn't fit your body, the consequences go beyond discomfort.
        Explore how specific dimensional mismatches lead to pain in different areas.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <a href="/knee-pain-seat-depth" class="group card-hub flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
          <div class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-accent text-primary">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 10h16M4 14h16M4 18h16" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-medium text-heading mb-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
          Knee Pain & Seat Depth
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground flex-1 mb-4">
          How insufficient seat depth creates pressure points behind the knees and causes circulation issues for tall users.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-primary">
          Learn more
          <svg class="ml-2 h-4 w-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/back-pain-spine-height" class="group card-hub flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
          <div class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-accent text-primary">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v18m6-18v18M3 9h18M3 15h18" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-medium text-heading mb-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
          Back Pain & Spine Height
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground flex-1 mb-4">
          Why lumbar support positioned for average users creates misalignment and chronic back pain for taller individuals.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-primary">
          Learn more
          <svg class="ml-2 h-4 w-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/leg-pain-circulation" class="group card-hub flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
          <div class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-accent text-primary">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-medium text-heading mb-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
          Leg Pain & Circulation
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground flex-1 mb-4">
          The relationship between seat height, chair cylinder length, and blood flow issues in the legs.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-primary">
          Learn more
          <svg class="ml-2 h-4 w-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-secondary/50 border border-border">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-medium text-heading mb-3">Foundation Reading</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm mb-4">
          Before diving into specific pain points, understand the fundamental problem.
        </p>
        <a href="/why-standard-chairs-dont-fit" class="link-internal text-sm">
          Why Standard Office Chairs Don't Fit Tall People →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
